<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Joke of the Day</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container p-5">
    <div class="bg-success p-5 text-center">
      <h2>A joke a day keeps the doctor away</h2>
      <p>If you joke wrong way, your teeth have to pay. (Serious)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center" >
      <div class="justify-content-center w-75 p-5">
        <p><%= joke %></p>
        <hr class="divider">

        <form method="POST" action="/jokes/<%= id %>/vote" class="text-center">
          <button type="submit" name="voteType" value="dislike" class="btn btn-primary">This is Funny!</button>
          <button type="submit" name="voteType" value="like" class="btn btn-success">This is not Funny.</button>
        </form>

      </div>


    </div>
  </div>
